            <title><![CDATA[GitHub Workshop Wikiへようこそ]]></title>
            <link>https://moshimoshipandasan.github.io/GitHub-demo/blog/welcome</link>
            <guid>https://moshimoshipandasan.github.io/GitHub-demo/blog/welcome</guid>
